02:04.225 --> 02:05.757
Dispatcher : This is an Amber

02:05.759 --> 02:08.794
alert message from the west
Virginia patrol department.

02:08.795 --> 02:13.332
A child abduction occurred at
3:00 pm yesterday in the town

02:13.334 --> 02:15.667
of castle rock, Wyoming county.

02:15.669 --> 02:20.172
