are giving me the creeps.

02:34.388 --> 02:35.721
We're almost there.

02:35.723 --> 02:37.523
Yeah, right.

02:37.525 --> 02:40.192
You've been saying that for the
past 100 miles, Blake blackman.

02:40.194 --> 02:41.360
Oh, we're in a grumpy mood.

02:41.362 --> 02:42.227
I know.

02:42.229 --> 02:42.928
I'm sorry.

02:42.930 --> 02:45.197
I'm sorry.

02:45.199 --> 02:46.565
This headache is killing me.

02:46.567 --> 02:48.200
We're not far from castle rock.

02:48.202 --> 02:50.802
Maybe we could stop,
grab some lunch.

02:50.804 --> 02:51.670
Oh, babe.

02:51.672 --> 02:52.571
Great.

02:52.573 --> 02:53.539
I have no cell signal.

02:53.541 --> 02:55.207
It's just the area.

02:55.209 --> 02:56.808
Great.

02:56.810 --> 03:00.245
Cabin in the middle of nowhere
with no cell signal, no cable.

03:00.247 --> 03:01.580
And lots of sex.

03:01.582 --> 03:02.414
Hmm.

03:02.416 --> 03:03.582
