03:13.194 --> 03:14.293
So this is it, right?

03:14.295 --> 03:15.260
This is it, baby.

03:15.262 --> 03:18.430
Castle rock?

03:18.432 --> 03:21.333
Hmm.

03:21.335 --> 03:25.237
Gosh, what happened here?

03:25.239 --> 03:27.439
I guess that's all that's left
after the big mudslide buried

03:27.441 --> 03:29.675
