03:29.677 --> 03:30.709
It's creepy.

03:30.711 --> 03:31.510
So sad.

03:35.849 --> 03:36.748
Yeah.

03:36.750 --> 03:38.250
Sherman mentioned it.

03:38.252 --> 03:41.820
It's a ghost town.

03:41.822 --> 03:44.723
Looks like we won't
be eating lunch here.

03:49.597 --> 03:51.330
Hey, honey.

03:51.332 --> 03:52.431
Yup.

03:52.433 --> 03:53.732
Almost there.

03:53.734 --> 03:56.935
Yeah, it's pretty nice up here.

03:56.937 --> 03:59.538
I know, it's hit or miss.

03:59.540 --> 04:00.806
Um-hmm.

04:00.808 --> 04:01.740
