Seriously--

10:10.110 --> 10:11.343
-no, it's not.
- --It wasn't funny.

10:11.345 --> 10:13.078
It's, I don't know,
kind of exciting.

10:13.080 --> 10:13.912
No.

10:13.914 --> 10:14.913
I like it.

10:14.915 --> 10:15.747
Yes, you do.

10:15.749 --> 10:18.083
Stop it.

10:18.085 --> 10:19.618
Stop it..

10:35.035 --> 10:35.867
Blake.

10:35.869 --> 10:36.801
Blake.

10:36.803 --> 10:38.136
Huh.

10:38.138 --> 10:39.638
Did you hear that?

10:39.640 --> 10:41.706
It's the wind.

10:41.708 --> 10:43.408
