13:40.086 --> 13:41.085
Give me a couple days.

13:41.087 --> 13:42.153
Uh, I'll give you a call.

14:01.308 --> 14:03.208
Is sherman gonna be worried
that you're not writing?

14:03.210 --> 14:06.044
Ah, sherman needs
to get over it.

14:06.046 --> 14:09.047
You're gonna be in
trouble with sherman.

14:09.049 --> 14:12.016
Ah, trouble with sherman--
trouble with sherman.

14:12.018 --> 14:14.118
I got trouble with you is
who I've got trouble with.

14:18.091 --> 14:22.460
Texting the wrong guy
can be very dangerous.

14:25.899 --> 14:29.400
You gonna be a good girl, hmm?

14:29.402 --> 14:35.340
