15:30.931 --> 15:31.996
She wants to go out
all the time now.

15:31.998 --> 15:33.531
No way.
I'm not risking it.

15:33.533 --> 15:36.401
Put her on a leash.

15:36.403 --> 15:39.337
Yeah, I guess.

15:39.339 --> 15:41.239
