ball that she brought.

15:41.241 --> 15:43.241
Did you see it?

15:43.243 --> 15:44.142
No.

15:44.144 --> 15:45.009
She's obsessed about it.

15:45.011 --> 15:46.644
Where'd she find it?

15:46.646 --> 15:48.646
In the woods, I guess.

15:48.648 --> 15:50.648
Come here, you.

15:50.650 --> 15:52.517
When you goin' into town?

15:52.519 --> 15:54.252
Not today, maybe tomorrow.

15:54.254 --> 15:57.655
I think I'm going
to do some sketches

15:57.657 --> 15:59.590
for that client of mine.

15:59.592 --> 16:01.192
And I still have
those headaches.

16:01.194 --> 16:02.627
I'm kind of worried.

16:02.629 --> 16:05.563
Why don't you go have
a doctor check it out?

16:05.565 --> 16:06.431
Where?

16:06.433 --> 16:08.399
In ghost town?

16:08.401 --> 16:12.003
You'll be able to
find somebody in there.

16:12.005 --> 16:14.305
I guess.

16:14.307 --> 16:17.175
Maybe tomorrow when
i go for groceries.

16:24.017 --> 16:25.383
Go get it, girl.

16:27.721 --> 16:29.220
Good girl.

16:29.222 --> 16:30.054
Come here.

16:30.056 --> 16:31.656
Good girl!

16:31.658 --> 16:32.690
Go!

16:36.596 --> 16:37.562
Good girl.

16:37.564 --> 16:39.130
Give it to me.

16:39.132 --> 16:40.098
Ready?

16:40.100 --> 16:41.065
Go!

16:41.067 --> 16:43.534
Go get it!

16:43.536 --> 16:44.369
Go!

16:47.073 --> 16:48.072
What are you looking at?

17:02.655 --> 17:04.655
Babe!

17:04.656 --> 17:05.656
Hey!

17:05.657 --> 17:07.657
Babe!

17:07.660 --> 17:08.593
Babe!

17:08.595 --> 17:09.426
Babe!

17:09.429 --> 17:10.795
What's wrong?

17:10.797 --> 17:11.695
-There's someone out there!
-What do you mean!

17:11.698 --> 17:13.196
