17:27.280 --> 17:28.679
Nothin'.

17:28.681 --> 17:30.615
Blake, I'm telling you.

17:30.617 --> 17:32.116
Someone is out there.

17:32.118 --> 17:33.184
I threw the ball and
someone threw the ball

17:33.186 --> 17:34.318
back at me from the woods!

17:34.320 --> 17:35.520
I don't have time.

17:35.522 --> 17:36.754
I need to go back
inside and write!

17:36.756 --> 17:38.256
You don't give a damn, do you?

17:38.258 --> 17:39.323
What do you want
from me, Angie?

17:39.325 --> 17:40.158
I searched!

17:40.160 --> 17:41.459
There's nothing!

17:41.461 --> 17:42.693
I told you to keep that
damn dog on a leash!

17:42.695 --> 17:44.195
You know what?

17:44.197 --> 17:47.365
Forget it.

17:47.367 --> 17:48.533
Come on.

17:51.704 --> 17:54.238
What are you doing?

17:54.240 --> 17:55.239
Angie, it's getting dark!

18:01.581 --> 18:02.413
Brandi!

18:32.545 --> 18:33.578
Who is that?

18:38.618 --> 18:41.185
Brandi!
Just come here!

18:41.187 --> 18:42.353
Oh, my god, girl!

18:48.495 --> 18:53.297
Oh, Brandi, I'm gonna kill you!

18:53.299 --> 18:56.234
Come here, girl.

18:56.236 --> 18:57.602
Where were you?

19:09.182 --> 19:10.148
How's your headache?

19:10.150 --> 19:10.748
