19:14.220 --> 19:15.820
What's that?

19:15.822 --> 19:17.221
Nothing.

19:17.223 --> 19:18.723
Something I'm working on.

19:18.725 --> 19:20.258
Look, I'm sorry.

19:20.260 --> 19:20.892
