19:20.894 --> 19:22.460
Yeah, you do.

19:22.462 --> 19:24.295
I-- I just think the
pressure's getting to me.

19:24.297 --> 19:26.564
--What are you
talking about, Blake?

19:26.566 --> 19:27.598
You're a great writer.

19:27.600 --> 19:28.399
You'll be able to write again.

19:28.401 --> 19:29.300
I mean about us.

19:32.739 --> 19:35.306
I've been thinking.

19:35.308 --> 19:37.308
It's time.

19:37.310 --> 19:39.744
We just can't do this anymore.

19:39.746 --> 19:40.545
We can't.

19:44.384 --> 19:45.416
It's not fair to her.

19:45.418 --> 19:46.884
It's not fair to me.

19:46.886 --> 19:48.819
You can't choose who
you fall in love with.

19:48.821 --> 19:56.594
