illustrator having

20:04.604 --> 20:05.703
an affair with a married guy.

20:08.541 --> 20:14.412
You know what-- what's
the sad part about this

20:14.414 --> 20:16.681
is I was one of
those women who would

20:16.683 --> 20:18.449
say I would never do that.

20:18.451 --> 20:22.987
