doesn't get out, please.

21:42.935 --> 21:43.768
Ok, I'm going.

21:43.770 --> 21:46.971
Love you.

21:46.973 --> 21:49.040
Love you too.

21:49.042 --> 21:50.808
And follow the GPS.

21:50.810 --> 21:51.676
