22:09.996 --> 22:11.629
--This is Claire blackman.

22:11.631 --> 22:14.398
Leave your name and
number at the beep.

22:14.400 --> 22:18.536
Claire, it's me.

22:18.538 --> 22:20.504
Call me when you get this.

22:20.506 --> 22:21.105
