Thanks.

22:54.407 --> 22:55.706
Authorities declined

22:55.708 --> 22:57.541
to go on camera that
in a statement released

22:57.543 --> 23:00.010
this morning, sheriff
Albert McFadden announced

23:00.012 --> 23:02.113
that no leads have
developed, nor have

23:02.115 --> 23:04.682
any suspects been targeted.

23:04.684 --> 23:07.785
